        <methods>
            <methodStep>
                <description>
                    <para>Standard woodland National Vegetation Classification (NVC) survey methodology was used to collect this data. Woodland communities were identified by eye and mapped, supported by sample quadrats and target notes.</para>
                </description>
            </methodStep>
            <qualityControl>
                <description>
                    <para>Data was collected by trained personnel, digitised by contractors, validated by Countryside Council for Wales&apos; (CCW) Knowledge Management Group, corrections made by contractors, validated again by CCW Knowledge Management Group, corrections made in-house in conjunction with Woodland Ecologist.</para>
                </description>
            </qualityControl>
